snippet.title: Yunyun Syndrome!? Rhythm Psychosis 2025 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Psychological X Cute X Rhythm Adventure Game
""Yunyun Syndrome!? Rhythm Psychosis"" release has been delayed to 2025.

For those awaiting the release,
Please keep the game wishlisted and stay strong 😭
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2914150/

📡⚡About Yunyun Syndrome!? Rhythm Psychosis ⚡📡
A rhythm adventure game about a psychotic hikikomori girl - also an avid anonymous poster - who corrupts the world with her severe brain rot from listening to too many denpa songs.
Yun-Yun all over this world.
